comment3.target=void\ reset()
comment3.text=\n\ Resets\ the\ current\ score\ to\ 0,\ copying\ it\ to\ highScore\ first\ if\ it's\n\ a\ new\ record.\ \ Called\ at\ the\ start\ of\ each\ new\ PlayingState.\n
