comment4.text=\n\ Updates\ highScore\ if\ the\ current\ score\ exceeds\ it.\n\ Called\ by\ GameOverState.enter()\ to\ freeze\ the\ best\ score\ for\ display.\n\ reset()\ already\ does\ this,\ but\ GameOverState\ calls\ this\ separately\n\ for\ clarity.\n
